(22, 1, '2016-05-23 13:36:30', '2016-05-23 13:36:30', 'There are many different homes for sale in Charleston, SC that have a wide variety of features, but nothing is more important than feeling comfortable in your own home. This feeling is created through thoughtful design, amenities and confidence in the quality of the build. Crescent Homes puts comfortable living at the top of their priority list with all this and more.\r\n<h2>Living in Crescent Homes Communities</h2>\r\nComfort, safety and security in a natural environment is what Crescent Homes strives for with every community they build. Comfort and safety come in the superior construction techniques used by Crescent Homes'' builders. Security comes in carefully selected locations and community design. Each location is well thought out to offer the upmost privacy while still keeping you connected to your neighbors.\r\n\r\nEvery time Crescent Homes breaks ground on a new home, they make a promise to the buyer that they will get a home that holds its value for years to come. This provides security knowing that you''ve made a sound investment for your family. Performance and price are perfectly balanced for an affordable, comfortable home full of amenities in a neighborhood that you''re proud to call home.\r\n<h2>Crescent Homes Features and New Home Amenities</h2>\r\nYour home is your cocoon in a world that’s full of hustle and bustle. Crescent Homes creates structures that offer the highest level of comfort and the latest new home amenities that improve the livability and value of each structure. Crescent Homes features include:\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li>Ample energy efficient features at no extra charge</li>\r\n   <li>Eco-friendly construction</li>\r\n  <li>Custom design options</li>\r\n  <li>Guaranteed energy savings</li>\r\n  <li>Crown molding</li>\r\n  <li>Full window casings</li>\r\n  <li>Tray ceilings</li>\r\n  <li>Recessed lighting</li>\r\n  <li>Energy efficient appliances</li>\r\n  <li>Tight construction for a cleaner, healthier home</li>\r\n   <li>Home buyers warranty</li>\r\n   <li>Maintenance manual</li>\r\n   <li>Community amenities like swimming pools, walking trails, parks and more</li>\r\n  <li>Solid customer service long after the sale</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ol>\r\n  <li>test</li>\r\n   <li>test</li>\r\n   <li>test</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p class="_mce_tagged_br">When it comes to creature comforts no one does it better than Crescent Homes. From the second you enter the community it’s clear that attention to detail and an understanding of what buyers are looking for go into each home and all the shared spaces. When comfortable living in Charleston, SC is what you want, you can rest assured that Crescent Homes will deliver.</p>', '7 CHARLESTON RESTAURANTS FOR AN EVENING WITH THE FAMILY', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '7-charleston-restaurants-for-an-evening-with-the-family', '', '', '2016-07-12 18:29:48', '2016-07-12 18:29:48', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?p=22', 0, 'post', '', 0),
